        <property name="styleSheet">
         <string notr="true">QLabel {
    /* Темный фон с синим отливом */
    background-color: rgba(20, 30, 45, 180); 
    
    /* Тонкая синяя рамка, как у кнопок */
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 223, 255, 60); 
    border-radius: 8px;
    
    /* Текст внутри */
    color: #FFFFFF;
    font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
        border-color: #00DFFF;
    background-color: rgba(30, 45, 65, 200);
    /* Отступы текста от краев квадратика */
    padding: 10px 5px;
}
</string>
        </property>
        <property name="text">
         <string>SYSTEM OVERVIEW
The HandTracker Control System is an advanced human-computer interaction interface designed to bridge the gap between
physical movement and digital execution. By leveraging real-time computer vision via OpenCV and high-fidelity landmark
detection through MediaPipe, this software interprets hand orientations as precise system commands. Whether you are
managing media playback or adjusting audio levels, the system eliminates the need for peripheral contact, providing
a seamless, touchless experience.</string>
        </property>
       </widget>
       <widget class="QLabel" name="label_8">
        <property name="geometry">
         <rect>
          <x>82</x>
          <y>250</y>
          <width>771</width>
          <height>151</height>
         </rect>
        </property>
        <property name="minimumSize">
         <size>
          <width>771</width>
          <height>151</height>
         </size>
        </property>
        <property name="maximumSize">
         <size>
          <width>771</width>
          <height>151</height>
         </size>
        </property>
        <property name="styleSheet">
         <string notr="true">QLabel {
    /* Темный фон с синим отливом */
    background-color: rgba(20, 30, 45, 180); 
    
    /* Тонкая синяя рамка, как у кнопок */
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 223, 255, 60); 
    border-radius: 8px;
    
    /* Текст внутри */
    color: #FFFFFF;
    font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
        border-color: #00DFFF;
    background-color: rgba(30, 45, 65, 200);
    /* Отступы текста от краев квадратика */
    padding: 10px 5px;
}
</string>
        </property>
        <property name="text">
         <string>HOW IT WORKS
To begin, ensure your camera is active and lighting is sufficient for hand landmark visibility. The engine processes your hand's
geometry in real-time: forming a Fist acts as a binary toggle to play or pause your current track, while rapid Horizontal Swipes
allow for effortless navigation between media files. For fine-grained adjustments, the system monitors the distance between
your index finger and thumb, translating the proximity into a Dynamic Volume scale.</string>
        </property>
       </widget>
       <widget class="QLabel" name="label_9">
        <property name="geometry">
