    font-weight: 600;
        border-color: #00DFFF;
    background-color: rgba(30, 45, 65, 200);
    /* Отступы текста от краев квадратика */
    padding: 10px 5px;
}
</string>
        </property>
        <property name="text">
         <string>CALIBRATION &amp; BACKGROUND MODE
For the most intuitive experience, navigate to the Settings menu to synchronize the tracker with your environment. Users can
toggle Mirror Mode to align on-screen feedback with natural movements or adjust the Detection Confidence thresholds
to filter out background noise in complex environments. Note that closing the window minimizes the app to the System Tray 
to ensure persistent gesture control; use the tray icon menu to fully exit the software.</string>
        </property>
